记者回忆与李文亮的对话：他自称是个小医生。
Reporter recalled the dialogue with Li Wenliang: he claimed to be a small doctor.
南方都市报                      。
Southern Metropolis Daily.
南方都市报。
Southern Metropolis Daily.
南都，换一种方式。
Nandu, a different way.
2月7日凌晨，武汉市中心医院发布消息，该院眼科医生李文亮，在抗击新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎疫情工作中不幸感染，经全力抢救无效，于2月7日凌晨2点58分去世，该院深表痛惜和哀悼。
In the early morning hours of February 7, Wuhan Central Hospital announced that Li Wenliang, an ophthalmologist at the hospital, had died at 2.58 a.m. on February 7 after suffering from an unfortunate infection in the course of fighting pneumonia infected with a new coronavirus.
当日中午，中纪委官网称，经中央批准，国家监委决定派出调查组赴武汉，就群众反映的涉及李文亮医生有关问题作全面调查。
At noon on the same day, CNC reported that, with the approval of the central government, the NNSC decided to send an investigation team to Wuhan to make a comprehensive investigation into the mass reaction involving Dr. Li Wenliang.
在此之前的一天，我就得到了他病危的消息。
The day before, I had news that he was dying.
当时，我的第一反应是“不太可能吧”，毕竟就在几天前，他还在微信上告诉我：“应该没有生命危险，大约半个月后能恢复大部分肺功能。
My first reaction was "unlikely," after all, just a few days ago, when he told me in a microphone message: "There should be no risk to life, most lung function will be restored in about half a month.
”随着越来越多信源的出现，我开始心慌，赶快给李文亮医生打电话、发微信，并通过短信留言，同时向武汉市中心医院的几个朋友核实。
As more and more sources appeared, I began to panic, phoning and sending messages to Dr LiWenLiang as well as checking with several friends at Wuhan Central Hospital.
不过，李文亮医生的微信再也没有发来任何回复。
However, Dr. Lee Wenliang's message did not send any response.
李文亮医生。
Dr. Lee Man-liang.
1月30日下午，在网上引发大量关注后，我联系上了李文亮医生。
On the afternoon of Jan. 30, after a lot of online attention, I contacted Dr. Liang.
当时是我第一次听到这位“吹哨人”的真实名字。
It was the first time I had heard the real name of the whistler.
在此之前，他一直是匿名接受媒体采访，在新闻报道中也是化名。
Prior to that, he had been interviewed anonymously by the media, in the news is also a pseudonym.
为了提前做好采访功课，拿到联系方式后，我曾反复寻找这位医生的公开资料，却发现关于他的信息实在有限。
In order to do a good job ahead of time interview, get contact information, I have repeatedly looked for this doctor's public information, but found that information about him is really limited.
通过关键词搜索，我终于在武汉市中心医院官网找到一篇《第三季文明职工新鲜出炉》的文章。
Through the keyword search, I finally found an article in Wuhan City Central Hospital Official Website "the third season of the new civilized workers" article.
这篇文章发布于2015年10月15日，文章列出了20名获奖员工，其中包括“李文亮（眼科）”。
The article, published Oct. 15, 2015, lists 20 winning employees, including "Lee Wenliang (Ophthalmology)."
当日16时32分，李文亮医生通过了我的微信添加好友验证。
On the same day, at 16: 32, Dr. Lee Wenliang passed my micro-letter to add friend verification.
简单自我介绍后，我把一篇司法机关发布的评价武汉被训诫者“应予宽容”的文章转发给他。
After briefly introducing myself, I forwarded to him an article published by a judicial organ evaluating the "tolerance" of Wuhan admonished people.
约半个小时后，他回复了两个字：“谢谢”，然后又补充道：“感谢网友的支持，感谢记者朋友的报道。
About half an hour later, he replied with two words: "Thank you," and then added, "Thanks for the support and thanks for the report.
”李文亮的朋友圈。
Li Wenliang's circle of friends.
因为李文亮在病房内不便通话，我们一直通过微信打字，断断续续聊了1个小时，主要采访了他在同学群里发布信息后被训诫，以及接诊患者时被感染的经过。
Because Li Wenliang is inconvenient in the ward, we have been typing through micro-letters, intermittent chat for an hour, mainly interviewed him in the class after the release of information, and the patient was infected when receiving treatment.
回想起来，李文亮医生当时身体状况似乎还不错。
In retrospect, Dr. Li Wenliang seemed to be in good health.
他说自己“精神状态好了一些，可以断续打字”，“估计半个月应该可以大部分恢复，我还是比较乐观的。
He said he was "in better shape and can type intermittently." "I think half a month should do most of the recovery, but I'm optimistic.
”聊天中，李文亮医生一直很温和，唯有两次特意用了感叹号。
"In the conversation, Dr LiWenLiang has been very gentle, only two times deliberately used exclamation mark.
一次是他说，“网上有人说我被吊销执照是错误的，需要澄清！”另一次是，“恢复以后还是上一线，疫情还在扩散，不想当逃兵！”1月30日20时，我将聊天内容匆忙整理成一篇千字左右的对话稿件。
"Some people on the Internet said I was being stripped of my license was wrong and needed to be clarified," he said. Another time, "After the recovery is still on the front line, the epidemic is spreading, do not want to be a deserter!
稿件编发过程中，我抱着试试看的心态问李医生能不能发一张工作照，作为文章配图。
Manuscripts in the process, I try to look at the mentality of Dr. Li can be issued a work photos, as a map of the article.
随后，他发来一张戴口罩工作时的自拍图，并回复说：“哈哈，只有这个……没怎么拍”。
He then sent a self-portrait of himself at work wearing a mask and replied, "Ha ha, only this... not much."
采访截图。
Interview screenshot.
这张自拍照成了我们略显拘谨采访的一个转折点。
This self-portrait marks a turning point in our somewhat formal interview.
我发现，这位严谨专业的医学博士也有生活化的一面。
I found that this rigorous and professional doctor of medicine also has a life-changing side.
他在后续的聊天中坦承，“生病后有段时间很难熬，吃了安眠药都睡不着，总在胡思乱想。
In a follow-up chat, he admitted, "There was a time when I was sick and I couldn't sleep with my sleeping pills.
不过，后来慢慢调整就好一些了。
But then it was better to tweak it slowly.
必须积极面对。
It must be confronted positively.
”在谈到关于他的公开资料较少时，他回复：“我是小医生，不是专家教授，没有什么履历。
When he spoke about the paucity of public information about him, he replied: "I'm a doctor, not an expert, and I don't have a curriculum vitae.
”他还提到，“爱人和孩子不在身边，我每天都会爱人微信视频聊天，她们都会给我加油鼓励。
"He also mentioned," I love you and my kids are not around. I love them every day by video chat, and they cheer me up.
”李文亮的朋友圈。
Li Wenliang's circle of friends.
在李文亮医生此前开放的朋友圈里，我曾看到他的微信个性签名是“理论是灰色的 生命之树常青”。
In the circle of friends Dr. Lee had previously opened, I had seen his micro-letter signature "Theory is the Grey Tree of Life".
他曾在新年到来前发出这样一条信息——2019年12月31日22时30分，李文亮医生发了四道菜的图片，分别是炭烤猪颈肉、泰式酸甜鸡肉、煎鱼丸、炒空心菜。
At 2230 hours on December 31, 2019, Dr Lim sent out pictures of four courses: roast pig-neck meat, Thai-style sour-and-sweet chicken, fried fish balls and fried cabbage.
李文亮医生当时配发的文字是，“不出意外的话，这四个小菜就是我在2019的最后一顿晚饭了。
Dr Liang's accompanying words were, "Not surprisingly, these four side dishes are my last supper in 2019."
如果一会（儿）我意外饿了，那这就是倒数第二顿。
If I'm accidentally hungry for a while, it's the penultimate meal.
新的一年，加油减肥。
The new year, refueling weight loss.
”而在更早之前的2012年12月，他在一条微博里写道：“朋友们，从今天起你们也许就联系不到我了，因为我要去拯救地球了”。
Earlier, in December 2012, he wrote in a microblog: "My friends, you may not be able to reach me from today because I am going to save the earth."
